## Error Handling and Recovery

```mermaid
graph TD
    start[Start Pipeline] --> detect[CA Drop Detection]
    detect -->|error| logError1[Log Error<br/>Continue monitoring]
    detect -->|success| monitor[Price Monitoring]
    
    monitor -->|error| reconnect[Reconnect Stream<br/>Retry with backoff]
    reconnect --> monitor
    monitor -->|success| evaluate[Evaluate Signals]
    
    evaluate -->|error| logError2[Log Error<br/>Skip evaluation]
    evaluate -->|success| checkRisk[Risk Check]
    
    checkRisk -->|failed| logRejection[Log Rejection<br/>Continue monitoring]
    checkRisk -->|passed| execute[Execute Trade]
    
    execute -->|error| handleExecError[Handle Execution Error<br/>Update circuit breaker<br/>Retry if appropriate]
    handleExecError -->|retry| execute
    handleExecError -->|abort| logError3[Log Error<br/>Alert user]
    execute -->|success| trackPosition[Track Position]
    
    trackPosition -->|error| logError4[Log Error<br/>Manual intervention]
    trackPosition -->|success| manageExit[Manage Exit]
    
    manageExit -->|error| logError5[Log Error<br/>Continue monitoring]
    manageExit -->|success| complete[Complete]
    
    logError1 --> monitor
    logError2 --> checkRisk
    logRejection --> monitor
    logError3 --> monitor
    logError4 --> manageExit
    logError5 --> monitor
```

